                    <h3 class="h6 mt-4">Response Structure</h3>
                    <p>Artifacts API endpoints return JSON with nested URL objects and comprehensive tags:</p>
                    <pre class="bg-dark text-white p-3 rounded"><code>{
    "artifacts": [
        {
            "uuid": "0192e554-352c-71d5-b110-84521efd92f9",
            "filename": "LORES.zip",
            "datePublished": {
                "year": 1984,
                "month": 5,
                "day": 22
            },
            "postedDate": "2024-11-01T12:25:54.092115+11:00",
            "size": {
                "formatted": "4k",
                "bytes": 4538
            },
            "description": "LO-RES in 1984.",
            "tags": {
                "category": "demo",
                "platform": "dos",
                "description": "a demo on MS Dos"
            },
            "urls": {
                "api": "/api/v1/artifact/ad2efee",
                "download": "/d/ad2efee",
                "html": "/f/ad2efee",
                "thumbnail": "/public/image/thumb/0192e554-352c-71d5-b110-84521efd92f9"
            }
        }
    ]
